{"tid":1838814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護肯罷工，我都肯課金落醫護工會。","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:07:48.000Z","uid":297672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87c97aaf06a7e496226b5bdc845ef17b55e1ee12","tid":1838814,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"<del>諗起月供護士姐姐我就興奮了</del><br />\n<br />\n呢個政府根本就係一撚堆癌細胞，你哋繼續接收啲大陸撚都只係打止痛退燒藥，治標唔治本。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再被人情緒勒索，啲撚屌病毒係因為政府冇撚把關先落到嚟，然後推你哋去死。<br />\n<br />\n我知，份糧真係好吸引，前途真係美滿。但無謂搵命搏，做人做鬼真係自己諗。<br />\n<br />\nbtw萬一我中招感染，我會自己報警。"},{"pid":"c4b66566499dd4582e69281e419dc90cde40c948","tid":1838814,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"特首已流亡海外?? 疫情失控, 港人自救有辦法??<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838790</a>"},{"pid":"a66346c836481221cacb8821fcf1e3fb7a2743cb","tid":1838814,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3f538f7ee7a35047108a2228c6200036f1f96124","tid":1838814,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"cdb84bdb3be50fab9bd67eb171f1f088ce05d30a","tid":1838814,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒</span>"}]}